 X-ray luminosities observed from\nhigh star-forming, low-mass galaxies. This is explained by the ejection of\nSNe-heated gas from the central regions of the halo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jun 2021 08:02:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-07"}
